courses.courseInfo: This qualification provides a pathway to the primary trades in the construction industry with the exception of plumbing. courses.courseTitle: Certificate III in Civil Construction Plant Operations
courses.courseInfo: This qualification will provide you with the practical skills and knowledge to undertake a range of manual labouring tasks and operate machinery on construction sites. You will learn about safe work practices, using equipment, tools and effective communication. You will also learn skills that will enable you to read plans, take measurements, drain sites, spread and compact materials manually, assist in excavation, operate small plant and organise your work.
